&lt;li&gt;Periodic meetings with Client to review overall progress, strategy, satisfaction and any new needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay abreast of all current agency accounts for reference in new business presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist agency leadership with research, and information gathering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and pursue sales and networking opportunities to grow client base&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend networking and marketing events as well as other seminars, expos, fairs, performances, etc. that present opportunities to promote the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to travel locally and out of town occasionally&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceed quarterly and annual sales quotas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
